---
title: Winning Pork Medallions with Potatoes, Brussels Sprouts, and Tarragon Cream Sauce
description: Ladies and gentlemen, I think we have a winner! These medallions might not bring you literal gold, but they’ll guarantee victory at dinnertime, at least. Made from pork tenderloin, the rounds get their name from their medal-like shape. They’re served with a crispy Brussels sprouts hash, potatoes, and an herby tarragon cream sauce—basically, a recipe that’s about as classic and accomplishment-worthy as can be.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/w18-r4-0eedd82f.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/w18-r4-29f6d546.pdf
servings: 2
author: HelloFresh
course: main course
